title: Complete coverage: Liberty's Samantha Peterson, Madelyn Conrad cruise to tennis title
text:
Liberty's Samantha Peterson, coach Leo Schnalzer and Madelyn Conrad after the Hurricanes' senior duo won the District 11 Class AAA doubles title. (Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 20, 2015 12:18 PM, updated October 20, 2015 2:47 PM 
Liberty seniors Samantha Peterson and Madelyn Conrad cruised to a 6-0, 6-1 victory over Freedom 's Natalie Sinai and Kaitlyn Swint in the District 11 Class AAA doubles final on Monday at Lehigh University. 
It was the second straight season the Hurricanes duo was in the final.
